long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is an extension that allows you to easily copy and paste pre-written prompts made by you! Be sure to pin the extension for easier access! Simply create a new prompt, give it a name and a value, and you'll have a shortcut to copy the pre-written text to your clipboard as many times as you need!
